{"tid":1171855,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭台銘失信於特朗普, 點會對台灣人守承諾?","createTime":"2019-05-26T04:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T07:22:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f91ff4a6c9ca96874b7fc80172e2c53a7e5005d1","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_669693_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_669693_0&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFI2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=094a7dfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_669693_0&h=40098f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_669693_0</a><br />\n<br />\n對於中國態度轉硬，以特朗普為達到目的，不擇手段的性格，即使美股大瀉，他亦不會因而讓步。事實上，郭台銘的鴻海集團，前年宣佈投資100億美元在威斯康辛州建立工廠，聘用當地員工生產液晶顯示（LCD）面板，特朗普亦有親自出席動土儀式，不過有外媒報道，工廠地盤至今仍一片荒蕪，今年初更傳出會縮減投資規模，只在美國做研發，而非生產。被郭台銘玩謝，特朗普對中國的信心就更小。"},{"pid":"0e1082b0dfcf7074f3dbe04c42f8ddb09799f579","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/94963.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F94963.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFI2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=6c7f12a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/94963.html</a><br />\n<br />\n31/01/2019<br />\n<br />\n台灣鴻海集團原計劃在美國威斯康星州興建液晶顯示屏廠房的計劃出現變化，可能縮減甚至擱置。<br />\n<br />\n鴻海集團董事長郭台銘2017年宣布計劃投資一百億美元，在美國威斯康星州設立生產液晶顯示屏的工廠，成為當地經濟復蘇的指標。鴻海此舉獲主張「美國優先」的美國總統特朗普歡迎，並形容投資計劃是「世界第八大奇蹟」。<br />\n<br />\n不過鴻海集團周三（30日）發表聲明，表示由於全球市場環境改變，公司有意將原來的建廠計劃改為設立科技研發中心，承諾會繼續在當地投資，以創造13,000個就業機會，但非原先設想的製造業勞工職位，而是主要招募工程師和研發人員。鴻海解釋，如果新廠房生產顯示屏，會令成本上升，難以與對手競爭。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有當地州議員質疑，鴻海違反創造就業的承諾，將令當地社區陷入困境。</strong>美國有線電視新聞網絡（CNN）報道，特朗普的製造業回流計劃出現適得其反結果已不是第一次。有分析指，受到中美貿易戰及蘋果手機在中國銷售疲弱影響，鴻海集團需要縮減投資計劃，或對特朗普尋求連任總統帶來打擊。<br />\n<br />\n(編輯：梁翠婷 陳妙芝)"},{"pid":"d06b1feaac676bd700d32e3eb26b42f4fd4c7970","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef6a44bd78354dacd5031a9a4ca3228ce640e31","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"政棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13d3d28fb92fa1e72e10b8ffadd937ae82f21d8","tid":1171855,"uid":46500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"賣台銘代表到台灣人咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508c9fcd48be1ac907d3d1f044ec253a82c8d0ee","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a13d3d28fb92fa1e72e10b8ffadd937ae82f21d8","tid":1171855,"uid":46500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:11:30.000Z","msg":"賣台銘代表到台灣人咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d91d35fe3de5268bab314cb99e075db3d96748","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"政棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1adc35eaf5aa953f0f91791a7fa249679beecf","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"推推政掍"},{"pid":"cb6285ca172894d31e735554874756ea814407b3","tid":1171855,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"血汗工廠"},{"pid":"755ef5e8faa1882506ea7f5d2c14e3c990a16f36","tid":1171855,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc